# Tap Tamak Backend — Cursor Rules

## Stack
- NestJS 10 + Prisma 5 + PostgreSQL 16
- JWT auth (access 15min, refresh 7d)
- All routes protected by default — use @Public() to opt out
- JwtAuthGuard + RolesGuard registered as global APP_GUARD

## Conventions
- Feature-based modules under src/modules/
- PrismaModule is @Global() — inject PrismaService directly, no repository layer
- All prices in KZT as Int (no decimals)
- All IDs are UUID (@id @default(uuid()))
- Use class-validator DTOs with whitelist: true
- API base: /api/v1

## Key rules
- Never use a repository pattern — Prisma IS the data access layer
- Always check idempotency in payment webhooks before processing
- Nearby cooks use Haversine formula via $queryRaw
- Webhook endpoints must be @Public() and validate provider signatures

## Refer to: docs/tap-tamak-backend.pdf for full schema, endpoints, and payment integration details